freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Burning aching pains in my feet and hands
Fever blisters (cold sores) outbreak on my mouth and nose. I find this happening more frequently since the second vaccine.
My sense of smell is off for the last three days

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Fever blister around my left nostril
Fever blister around my nose and swollen lymph nodes on the left side underneath my chin
